自2017年以来，这里开设了一家常春藤餐厅<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://theivycheltenhambrasserie.com/ |title=The Ivy Cheltenham |access-date=2019-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508003059/https://theivycheltenhambrasserie.com/ |archive-date=2019-05-08}}</ref> 并进行了修复。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Thomas |first1=Aled |title=How the Ivy wants to restore Montpellier Rotunda to its Regency glory |url=https://www.gloucestershirelive.co.uk/whats-on/whats-on-news/how-ivy-wants-restore-montpellier-768018 |accessdate=30 March 2020 |work=Gloucestershire Live |date=13 November 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116175927/http://www.gloucestershirelive.co.uk/whats-on/whats-on-news/how-ivy-wants-restore-montpellier-768018 |archive-date=16 November 2017}}</ref>

==建筑==
该建筑拥有[[石灰石|石灰石]]墙壁和铜屋顶。<ref name="nhle"/> 前立面有[[多立克柱式|多立克柱式]]的[[柱廊|柱廊]]，<ref name="nhle"/> 中央穹顶的中间有光线进入。房间高{{convert|56|ft}}，直径{{convert|54|ft}}<ref name="nhle"/>。

